VPS-LXC

How to Get Started:

$ git clone git://github.com/extofme/vps-lxc.git /vps
$ /vps/struct
$ mount -t cgroup lxc /vps/dev/vps-lxc
$ ln -s /vps/etc/profile.d/vps-lxc.sh /etc/profile.d
$ ln -s /vps/etc/bash_completion.d/vps-lxc /etc/bash_completion.d
$ . /etc/profile.d/vps-lxc.sh
$ . /etc/bash_completion.d/vps-lxc
$ vps-lxc help
